  <description>
    <p>Pancord is a cross-platform Vesktop Fork desktop app aiming to give you extra plugins but still give you a snappier Discord experience, with Equicord pre-installed.</p>
    <p>Which comes bundled with Venmic, a purpose-built library to provide functioning audio screenshare.</p>
  </description>
